Bashful, Doc, Dopey, Grumpy, Happy, Sleepy and Sneezy are back!
In the whimsical world of Jollywood, Queen Delightful relies on
seven brave heroes, the 7D, to keep the kingdom safe. Two novice
evil sorcerers, Grim and Hildy Gloom, plot to overthrow Jollywood
and steal the magic jewels in the 7D's mine. With seven distinct
and funny personalities, the 7D are there to save the day from
the Glooms' hapless schemes. The 7D must rescue Jollywood from
an eternal winter, retrieve the beloved Magic Mirror, and throw
a big surprise party for the Queen!

Produced by Walt Disney Television Animation.

The Magic Mirror is stolen by the Glooms and is replaced by an impostor.

Bashful becomes a masked vigilante named "The Big Bash".
